Package interfaces

Interface BarInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Bar
    public interface BarInterface
extends java.rmi.Remote
    Operational interface of a remote object of type Bar. It provides the functionality to access the Bar.
